{
  "stem": "7722.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 23.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I gave him the lard, and he gave us-- they had over there a dairy factory, and they gave us fresh-- fresh butter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I also did it-- I made out with him [INAUDIBLE] the kitchens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I gave each family their food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were-- each family had only one room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And sometimes they were four, six people to one room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I still-- I tried to give them-- they should be by themselves and not their own three times a week over there [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was very, very active, as I was at home, before the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was active.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Jabotinsky came to-- to our big town, to Rovno, not far from us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's about 30 some kilometers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I went over there to his speech.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I want to mention one thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't know exactly in the world they are the three best speaker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was Trotsky, Jabotinsky-- if I don't make a mistake-- Mussolini.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Those, they are the best.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If you could hear Jabotinsky talking, how do you-- how you didn't know nothing, you were ready to follow him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said he knew it was through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he told them, leave the-- leave the Galut.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If not, the Galut will-- will finish you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I wish we would-- we would listen to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Maybe there would have been more survivors today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was already when I was already self-employed already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was already when I was already in the twenties, I was already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was very, very active.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1947 and 1948 we were over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later on-- and later on they decided to liquidate there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because-- because they gave-- people starts leaving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
